{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-working-with-text/working-with-text-lesson-a","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Pogledajte i prateći video Kevina Powella o stihovima i naslovima HTML iznad.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"top-working-with-text","challengeType":15,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Nije mi jasno šta sledeći tekst prikazuje na stranici za HTML?</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;body>\n  Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor\n  incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.\n\n  Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris\n  nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.\n&#x3C;/body>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Izgleda kao dva pasusa teksta, pa se možete očekivati da će biti prikazani na taj način. Međutim, nije tako, kako vidite u rezultatima ispod:</p>\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowpaymentrequest=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"cp_embed_iframe \" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"300\" width=\"100%\" name=\"cp_embed_1\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://codepen.io/TheOdinProjectExamples/embed/xxrKqeV?height=300&amp;theme-id=dark&amp;default-tab=html%2Cresult&amp;slug-hash=xxrKqeV&amp;user=TheOdinProjectExamples&amp;name=cp_embed_1\" style=\"width: 100%; overflow:hidden; display:block;\" title=\"CodePen Embed\" loading=\"lazy\" id=\"cp_embed_xxrKqeV\"></iframe>\n<p>Kada pregledač naiđe na nove linije kao ove u HTML vašem, on će smanjiti te linije u samo jedan prostor. Rezultat ovog spajanja je da se sav tekst sastavi u jednu dugu liniju.</p>\n<p>Ako želite da kreirate pasus u HTML, morate koristiti funkciju pasusa, koja će dodati novi red nakon svakog vašeg pasusa. Funkcija pasusa je opisana oko sadržaja teksta i oznake <code>&#x3C;p></code>.</p>\n<p>Modifikovanje našeg prvobitnog primera korišćenjem elemenata paragrafa rešava problem:</p>\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowpaymentrequest=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"cp_embed_iframe \" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"300\" width=\"100%\" name=\"cp_embed_2\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://codepen.io/TheOdinProjectExamples/embed/mdwbmdp?height=300&amp;theme-id=dark&amp;default-tab=html%2Cresult&amp;slug-hash=mdwbmdp&amp;user=TheOdinProjectExamples&amp;name=cp_embed_2\" style=\"width: 100%; overflow:hidden; display:block;\" title=\"CodePen Embed\" loading=\"lazy\" id=\"cp_embed_mdwbmdp\"></iframe>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Odin","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-working-with-text/working-with-text-lesson-a"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Kako se razvija stih u HTML?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><code>&#x3C;h3>This is a paragraph&#x3C;/h3></code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>&#x3C;p>This is a paragraph&#x3C;/p></code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>&#x3C;strong>This is a paragraph&#x3C;strong></code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","tests":[],"title":"Rad sa tekstovima iz lekcije A","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":"yqcd-XkxZNM","videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/the-odin-project/#top-working-with-text","dashedName":"working-with-text-lesson-a","certification":"the-odin-project","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"top-working-with-text","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-working-with-text/working-with-text-lesson-b","prevChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-html-foundations/html-foundations-lesson-h","id":"637f4e5872c65bc8e73dfe27","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeTyp